 </code><code>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code>Amends the Election Code. Requires Voters Identification Cards for </code><code>those who do not have an acceptable photo ID. Sets forth requirements and </code><code>exemptions. Provides that any person desiring to vote shall present to the </code><code>judges of election for verification of the person's identity a </code><code>government-issued photo identification card or his or her Voter </code><code>Identification Card.</code><code>
